lth. The other members of the group are:</span></li></ol><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">1)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Professor Cornelius K</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">atona, Consultant Psychiatrist, Royal College of Psychiatrists and Helen Bamber Foundation</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">2)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Emma Mlotshwa, coordinator, Medical Justice</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">3)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Theresa Schleicher, casework manager, Medical Justice</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">4)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Natasha Tsangarides, research, Medical Justice</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">5)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span